OL,3,COctober is Black History Month, but is
OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year
OL,5,Cround?
OL,7,FData from multiple exam boards
OL,8,Fanalysed by The Guardian shows that
OL,9,Fjust 1 in 10 GCSE history pupils study
OL,10,Fmodules which mention black peoples'
OL,11,Fcontribution to Britain.
OL,13,FWatch Nick Smith's report ...
OL,15,F'The Black Curriculum' was founded by
OL,16,FLavinya Stennett in 2019, campaigning
OL,17,Ffor mandatory inclusion of black
OL,18,Fhistory in all schools and providing
OL,19,Feducational resources on the subject
OL,20,Ffor teachers.
